high_descs: Move to the trash can to the left of the fridge
Pick up the egg inside of the trash can
Turn left then move towards the microwave above the stove top
Place the egg in the microwave, cook it, pull it out then shut the microwave
Carry the egg to the left corner of the white table top
Place the egg on the table on the front left corner to the left of the salt
anns.task_desc: Place a heated egg on the table

high_descs: move to the bin to the left of the fridge
pick up a egg from the bin
move to the stove to the left of you
heat the egg in the microwave
move to the table to the left
put the egg on the table

high_descs: Turn right, take a few steps forward, and then turn right towards the grey bin.
Take out an egg from the grey bin.
Turn around, take a few steps forward, and then turn right towards the microwave above the stove.
Cook the egg inside the microwave and take it back out.
Turn around, walk towards the wall, turn right towards the trash bag on the floor, and then turn right to face a white table.
Place the egg to the right of the spatula on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked egg from the grey bin on to the table.
